(44940, 'zhTW', '寒冬風暴之中', '從塔上使用爪鉤，並沿著小徑爬上山頂。', '那邊，你應該可以從這裡直接越過去。這條路應該可以帶著你一路向上直達山頂。\n\n根據我的情報，你要的龍就在那邊。希望他們還有餘力協助你。', '', '', '', '', '', '', 31478),
(44922, 'zhTW', 'Inside the Winter Storm', 'Grapple across from the tower and climb to the top of the mountain path.', 'There, it looks like there\'s a good spot to launch to right across from here. This path should take you all the way to the top.\n\nAccording to my  intel, your dragons should be up there. Let\'s just hope that they\'re still in a state to help you.', '', '', '', '', '', '', 31478),
